Package gov.nasa.jpl.ammos.mpsa.aerie.merlinsdk.resources

Interface Resource<Model,​Dynamics>

  • Type Parameters:
    Model - The type of the information tracked by the resource's governing model.
    Dynamics - The type of dynamics governing this resource's behavior over time.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DiscreteResource<Model,​T>, RealResource<Model>
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
    @FunctionalInterface
public interface Resource<Model,​Dynamics>
    An assignment of a dynamics to a resource given the state of its governing model.
